title: Naybin
text: Naybin (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Nāybīn) is a village in <a href="Torkaman%20Rural%20District">Torkaman Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Urmia%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Urmia%20County">Urmia County</a>, <a href="West%20Azerbaijan%20Province">West Azerbaijan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 422, in 109 families.
